                        type="source" xml:id="d116fn1">Source: Reagan Library, <gloss
                            target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Intelligence Files, System IV Files, Box
                        H381, 40776–40800. Top Secret; [<hi rend="italic">handling restriction not
